{"tid":1313672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記協及攝記協再次發表聯合聲明","createTime":"2019-07-14T00:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T05:02:40.000Z","uid":212626,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"209b1a6170cf6623e16fdf064270253a7506df8e","tid":1313672,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:36:10.000Z","msg":"香港攝影記者協會及香港記者協會發表聯合聲明，指警方在《光復上水》遊行後的清場行動，多次推撞前線記者鏡頭及身軀，更加有記者被警員用警棍揮打，或以盾牌推撞，對此表示遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n聲明說，近期多次示威活動中，警方清場時都有推撞及辱罵記者的情況，<span style=\"color: red;\">協會多次發聲明，但情況未有改善</span>，促請警方正視警權問題，尊重新聞自由及記者採訪的職責。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又說，網上流傳有《香港01》記者及《法新社》記者被警察用警棍打傷，協會調查後確定並無相關事件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468238-20190714.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468238-20190714.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=6ee1ae4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468238-20190714.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7e161de6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468238-20190714.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ff6c1b87a1ccad9cc4129068b9de20b3feeda93d","tid":1313672,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:36:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c9218f9ab096c397bfed84071bd56903143aaa3","tid":1313672,"uid":259329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:37:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b0f9c64243f06e3857d9a1267348e9b45184fe6","tid":1313672,"uid":212626,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:38:00.000Z","msg":"香港攝影記者協會 香港記者協會<br />\n聯合聲明<br />\n<br />\n警方在昨日（7月13日）下午6時左右，於上水反水貨遊行後的清場行動期間，多次推撞前線記者的鏡頭和身軀，更有記者被警員以警棍揮打，或者以警盾連續推撞，本會表示遺憾，促警方正視警權問題，尊重傳媒的採訪權。<br />\n<br />\n清場期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">NOW新聞</span>一名攝影師手持大型攝錄拍攝，被一名身穿警方黑色背心的便衣警員，在後方衝前數步以警棍揮打大腿，幸而該攝影師及時退後避開。<br />\n<br />\n一名<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文匯報</span></span>記者在採訪時亦受警員攻擊，該記者身穿反光衣以及戴著寫有「記者」字眼的頭盔，但仍然被一名情緒激動的警員用圓盾揮打兩至三次。<br />\n<br />\n一名<span style=\"color: red;\">自由攝影記者</span>在警察清場期間，被幾名警員多次用盾牌推撞，更有警員不斷用警棍指嚇並逼近，該記者多次舉起記者證並澄清是記者，警員仍然向前逼近大叫，以及再以盾牌推撞。<br />\n<br />\n一名<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">東方日報</span></span>記者在拍攝期間，亦被警員用盾牌推撞兩次，並一度推開攝影機，以及質疑記者推撞警察，最後該警員自行離開。<br />\n<br />\n近期的多次示威活動中，警方進行清場時都有推撞和辱罵記者的情況，本會多次發出聲明但情況仍未有所改善，促請警方正視警權問題，尊重新聞自由以及記者在現場採訪的職責。<span style=\"color: red;\">另外網上流傳指有《香港01》記者以及《法新社》記者被警察用警棍打傷，經調查後本會確定並沒有相關事件，特此澄清。</span><br />\n<br />\n香港攝影記者協會<br />\n香港記者協會<br />\n2019年7月14日"},{"pid":"015715248e2b4396d640934a791b3ce557a24fcb","tid":1313672,"uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:38:14.000Z","msg":"文匯報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79777a374185775c12f540cd1f1d537c3098cf2f","tid":1313672,"uid":192776,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:39:30.000Z","msg":"文匯報都畀狗打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74609679531ac99596a53674ef025a369b531cb","tid":1313672,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:39:58.000Z","msg":"按錯負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2354cb7f69a6815d950031b4c164f6a4b49a3bc1","tid":1313672,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400eb92c126f317190146c2a5530220a3e4ff3aa","tid":1313672,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ce6e97f7bdd4ca05cd24d48377fae1a4b36b29","tid":1313672,"uid":6799,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:46:37.000Z","msg":"文匯報譴責暴力未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab814ef69dfd1cdc0b5e151e5e490b3305ad304c","tid":1313672,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:46:39.000Z","msg":"七個傳媒工會組織聯合發起<br />\n停止警暴．捍衛新聞自由<br />\n新聞界靜默遊行<br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂爭議觸發社會矛盾，在連串示威活動中，記者採訪多次被警方無理驅趕、推撞、辱罵，以至被警棍打傷、被布袋彈擊中，記者連自身安全亦受威脅，遑論要充分發揮第四權的角色，監察公權力運用。<br />\n<br />\n七個傳媒工會和組織發起「停止警暴。捍衛新聞自由」新聞界靜默遊行，以沉默表達我們的憤怒，要求警方遵從警例，配合傳媒採訪工作，尊重新聞自由；並要求行政長官林鄭月娥，履行競選時簽署《新聞自由約章》承諾，捍衛新聞自由。<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年7月14日 (星期日)<br />\n時間：上午10:30集合<br />\n集合地點：夏慤花園<br />\n終點：（途經警察總部）特首辦<br />\n服飾：黑衣（可自行決定穿戴反光衣）<br />\n<br />\n*歡迎現職或前新聞工作者、新聞系教職員及學生、大專校報編委參加<br />\n<br />\n香港記者協會 <br />\n香港攝影記者協會<br />\n獨立評論人協會 <br />\n大專新聞教育工作者聯席 <br />\n明報職工協會<br />\n壹傳媒工會<br />\n香港電台節目製作人員工會<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月11日<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D5sK7RE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD5sK7RE.jpg&h=06b66399&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n默默支持就得<br />\n今日主力沙田"},{"pid":"df3e6e5bff63b6da8274f323d3d5cb6db026972e","tid":1313672,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8dab6b0f54c02fd0b8d6aa02f941e02b98fcba","tid":1313672,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7600c77daf2322819fa6e5be1cb44831a77399d7","tid":1313672,"uid":151248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:54:40.000Z","msg":"文匯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdf23b8a562689603d851ba2b9a2d57d3d409b4","tid":1313672,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686559f80222be97e6b6e06d76756251a736e12f","tid":1313672,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c19eccbe50836eb905ec7aee2694f558fa6297","tid":1313672,"uid":264585,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a1ed3a6e1bd75895891ddee173c56d2b250058","tid":1313672,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:07:42.000Z","msg":"遺你老母憾咩<br />\n屌佢老母啦<br />\n獨立調查啦"},{"pid":"36aa5f7f6a33f5103b58c4e63024e3dfb1f6f94b","tid":1313672,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed15fe08c72abb4b7bb5a03379615855f0ac0784","tid":1313672,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"015715248e2b4396d640934a791b3ce557a24fcb","tid":1313672,"uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:38:14.000Z","msg":"文匯報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\